    "description": "四魂-X是以浩淼的银河系为舞台的点击式冒险解谜游戏——但全程无需任何点击操作！为了挖掘人类深陷宇宙战争泥沼的原因，踏上一场银河尺度的大冒险。就算是面对着宇宙级别的威胁，也别忘了抽出时间打一盘酣畅淋漓的弹珠。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About This Game</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1298270/extras/a0ebbd2f28a23186945c9bf4aaa145d9.poster.avif?t=1723800291\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1298270/extras/a0ebbd2f28a23186945c9bf4aaa145d9.webm?t=1723800291\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1298270/extras/a0ebbd2f28a23186945c9bf4aaa145d9.mp4?t=1723800291\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>达雅少校堪称是联邦最杰出的飞行员，在一次常规防卫行动期间，她收到了一条来自全人类的宿敌——罗尔人的神秘信息。以此为起点，达雅踏上了一段充满八九十年代动画的甜美回忆，横跨银河系的宏大冒险。探索光怪陆离的外星，邂逅古灵精怪的角色，最终揭露与罗尔人旷日持久的战争的真相。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1298270/extras/b094d1b42a53aaa6ae87ebb2140602bd.poster.avif?t=1723800291\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1298270/extras/b094d1b42a53aaa6ae87ebb2140602bd.webm?t=1723800291\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1298270/extras/b094d1b42a53aaa6ae87ebb2140602bd.mp4?t=1723800291\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>《四魂-X》的灵感源自点击式冒险解谜游戏的黄金时代，但并没有继承点击式操作的传统，而是提供了更加丝滑顺畅的游戏体验：无需徒劳地频繁狂点鼠标，无需尝试特定动作与场景、道具的排列组合，更无需朝着突兀的行动选项转轮干瞪眼。本作只提供了一个物品栏和一个互动键，只需与角色或其他目标互动即可推进剧情。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1298270/extras/eb0566d3db18627926a7376577b5f186.poster.avif?t=1723800291\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1298270/extras/eb0566d3db18627926a7376577b5f186.webm?t=1723800291\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1298270/extras/eb0566d3db18627926a7376577b5f186.mp4?t=1723800291\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>多种街机式迷你游戏点缀着四魂-X的冒险过程。在怀旧的纵版卷轴射击游戏中驱逐太空侵略者，在功能完整的弹珠台中炫耀自己的操作技巧。每个迷你游戏都有与之配套的剧情，在游玩的过程中甚至能体验到故事节奏的变换！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >核心要素</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>丝般顺滑的点击式冒险解谜体验——但不含任何点击成分<br></li><li>以易用性为主导的游戏体验设计贯穿全程<br></li><li>充满八九十年代动画风格的银河系大冒险<br></li><li>为推动叙事服务的多款街机式迷你游戏<br></li><li></li></ul>",
